	(title_block
		(title "ReefVolt SensorBuddy — Sensor Interfaces")
		(date "2026-04-18")
		(rev "0.1")
		(comment 1 "Isolated pH/ORP probes, NTC, 1-Wire, float switches")
		(comment 2 "ADM3260 isolation barrier + ADS1115 + OPA2376 buffer")
	)
	(lib_symbols
	)

	(text "Sensor Interfaces\n\nIsolated Probes (pH / ORP):\n  ADM3260ARSZ I2C isolator + isoPower → ISO_3V3 domain\n  OPA2376AIDR dual unity-gain buffer (2 channels)\n  ADS1115IDGST 16-bit differential ADC\n    AIN0/1: Probe A (BNC), AIN2/3: Probe B (BNC)\n  Mid-rail bias: 2× 100kΩ 0.1% divider + 0.1µF per channel\n  220Ω + 100pF output filter per buffer channel\n\nNTC Thermistors (×3):\n  3.3V → 10kΩ 0.1% fixed → STM32 ADC (PA0/PA1/PA4) → NTC → GND\n  0.1µF filter cap on each ADC input\n  Phoenix COMBICON 2-pos (1803277) per channel\n\n1-Wire DS18B20 (×2 buses):\n  STM32 USART2 (PA2) + USART3 (PA3), half-duplex\n  4.7kΩ pull-up, 100Ω series + 100pF damper\n  Phoenix COMBICON 3-pos (1803280) per bus\n  LwOW firmware library for ROM search + DS18B20\n\nFloat Switches (×4):\n  STM32 GPIO (PA5/PA6/PA7/PB0) with internal pull-up\n  100nF debounce cap per channel\n  Phoenix COMBICON 2-pos (1803277) per switch"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
